    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This car is in poor condition. The exterior has multiple dents, scratches, and visible rust in several areas. The interior shows heavy wear \u2014 the upholstery is worn through in places, and several trim pieces are damaged or missing. Mechanically, the car has known issues and will require significant repairs. Priced accordingly for a buyer who understands the work involved.",
